hosts.about:
Hello,
We are two hard-working creatives here in NY. She is a designer and I'm a photographer. We travel quite often and understand the importance of coming back to a nice relaxing home. We try very hard to make sure our home is a little oasis away from the city (sometimes the city can be over-whelming). But that's OK!  That's why we have nice amenities like the 15,000 BTU A/C unit for the summer and an apple TV! And we know the importance of getting around the city, we have to do it everyday. Positioning ourselves a block away from the 74th St/Roosevelt Ave express stop is KEY to getting around! 

We would be honored to have you as our guest. Tell me a little about yourself!
